## ğŸš€ **Deployment**

### **Render Platform Deployment**

The website is automatically deployed on [Render](https://render.com) with the following configuration:

```yaml
# render.yaml
services:
  - type: web
    name: environment-india
    env: node
    plan: free
    buildCommand: npm install
    startCommand: npm start
    envVars:
      - key: NODE_ENV
        value: production
```

**Live URL:** [https://env-gov-india.onrender.com](https://env-gov-india.onrender.com)

